<title>伊朗宣布：向美军“林肯”号航母发射4枚弹道导弹</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%86%9B%E2%80%9C%E6%9E%97%E8%82%AF%E2%80%9D%E5%8F%B7%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E5%8F%91%E5%B0%844%E6%9E%9A%E5%BC%B9%E9%81%93%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%B9</link>
